  <widget type="label" version="2.0.0">
    <name>Instructions</name>
    <text>HOW TO TEST:
1. loc:// Text Entry above should be ENABLED immediately on startup (no Enable Setting needed).
2. All other widgets (acsys://, ca://, etc.) start DISABLED — including the Table below.
3. Click "Enable Setting" in the toolbar, pick a duration → gated widgets (+ Table) enable.
4. Wait for the timer to expire → gated widgets disable; loc:// entry stays writable.</text>
    <x>10</x>
    <y>620</y>
    <width>680</width>
    <height>110</height>
    <foreground_color>
      <color name="Blue" red="0" green="0" blue="200">
      </color>
    </foreground_color>
